# Changelog — {{PROCESS_NAME}}

All notable changes to this process follow [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/).

## Versioning Rules

| Bump | When |
|---|---|
| MAJOR | Process fundamentally redesigned; scope boundary shift; purpose change; compliance framework change |
| MINOR | Steps added/removed; roles added/removed; artifacts added/removed; new recipe |
| PATCH | Step wording polish; TTL field refresh; new cases; typo fixes |

